defaultReview and make recommendations to the Executive Board on further development of BIS’s sustainability commitments, governance and activities to support its overall ambitions
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultContribute sustainability content to the BIS operational plan, business planning, developing and recommending sustainability business performance measures (where none exist).
default-
