defaultDevelop actions plans, overseeing implementation and monitoring performance across BIS in order to achieve greener government targets and measures set out in the Operational Plan
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultBenchmark BIS’s sustainability performance against partner organisations and peers.
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultCommunicate sustainability activities and plans to staff and, where relevant, external stakeholders 
